Description:
You arrive at the headquarters of the "Company of Overseas Trade" where a representative explains their operations on the island. 

They are distributing the island's riches globally, sometimes against the wishes of the natives, who are fiercely protective of their heritage. 

The company offers you a ship and a license to exploit the resources, provided you operate under the COT’s name.
